Package: popsicleR
Type: Package
Title: Pipeline of Preprocessing for Single Cell Experiment
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Francesco Grandi, Jimmy Caroli, Oriana Romano, Matteo Marchionni, Mattia Forcato and Silvio Bicciato
Maintainer: Francesco Grandi <francesco.grandi1993@unimore.it>
Description: Here we present popsicleR, a flexible R package aimed at providing most of the necessary quality controls and preliminary information for complete and detailed analysis of single cell RNA-seq data. In its workflow, popsicleR integrates all the pivotal steps necessary to assess sample quality, apply data tailored filters and perform doublets calculation and annotation analysis.
License: GPL3
Encoding: UTF-8
